<br>
Dark...Fear..Ebolt HG 1<br>
Dark Fear PET HG2<br>
Dark Fear Ebolt HG3<br>
Dark Fear Ebolt HG4<br>
Dark Ebolt HG5<br>
Dark HG6<br>
Basic idea is by the time that ebolt/fear is off, pet has mauled the first hill giant, and is working on 2nd...3rd...4th, ect ect.  The first time i did it, i walked away with a good 300pp.<br>
<br>
Takes most of a mana bar, like a druid that is quad kiting, it also takes a huge amount of room, But, with a decent pet, and enough mana, those hill giants will drop like so many tons of bricks.<br>
<br>
(note: i do not suggest you do this often, its no way to make friends...makes druids jealous <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  and groups angry at your greed...i did this only when it was me camping giants.)<br>
<br>
Jadedskeleton Vel'Mach<br>
